</section>
<section id="fs-idm216035520" class="problem-set-b">
<exercise id="fs-idm176858320">
<problem id="fs-idm224109424">
<para id="fs-idm199239744"><link class="lo-reference" document="m68082"/>Cinnamon Depot bakes and sells cinnamon rolls for $1.75 each. The cost of producing 500,000 rolls in the prior year was:</para>
<media id="fs-idm201908960" alt="Revenues $875,000, Direct materials $425,000, Direct labor $75,000, Manufacturing overhead (fixed) $125,000, Manufacturing overhead (variable) $90,000.">
